library(cutpointr)
library(tidyverse)

#read in combined file
meta <- read_tsv("../../../analyses/add-histologies/output/ALT PBTA oct 2021 (including all plates)-updated-hist-alt.tsv",
         guess_max = 1000)

#subset for HGG and non-HGG
hgat <- meta %>%
  filter(group == "HGAT")
non_hgat <- meta %>%
  filter(group == "non-HGAT")

#how many per group?
meta %>%
  group_by(group) %>%
  tally()

#run optimal cutpoint by group
